sentences: Submotion Orchestra are a seven piece band formed in 2009 in Leeds, Yorkshire, England.
Their debut LP Finest Hour was released on Ranking Records.
They have since released five full-length albums - Finest Hour (2011), Fragments (2012), Alium (2014), Colour Theory (2016), Kites (2018) - and two EPs - 1968 (2013) and III (2015).
